"People are under a lot of stress, houses are expensive and so is education, so many people are putting it off", says a young executive.
Other people can have children.
"But it's important to me to have my own money and time", says another young man in his early 20's.
Men and women cite their career, stress, and the cost of property and education as reasons why they are unable to have children.
